---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for Latin Addiction UK — how we handle your data when you use our website, checkout, and contact forms."
>

  <section class="bg-white px-5 py-14 md:px-8 md:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto prose-container">
      <h1 data-reveal class="font-display font-extrabold text-[clamp(2rem,5vw,3rem)] leading-[1.1] mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>

      <p data-reveal class="text-muted text-[0.92rem] mb-6">
        <strong class="text-dark">Latin Addiction UK Ltd</strong> ("we", "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This policy explains what data we collect and how we use it.
      </p>

      <h2 data-reveal class="font-display font-semibold text-[1.25rem] mt-8 mb-3">What we collect</h2>

      <h3 data-reveal class="font-display font-semibold text-[1.05rem] mt-6 mb-2">Contact form</h3>
      <p data-reveal class="text-muted text-[0.92rem] mb-4">
        If you use our contact form, we collect your name, email address, and message. This data is processed by <strong class="text-dark">Web3Forms</strong> and delivered to info@latinaddiction.co.uk. We use it only to respond to your enquiry.
      </p>

      <h3 data-reveal class="font-display font-semibold text-[1.05rem] mt-6 mb-2">Online payments</h3>
      <p data-reveal class="text-muted text-[0.92rem] mb-4">
        Payments are processed by <strong class="text-dark">SumUp</strong> via their Card Widget. Your payment card details are handled entirely by SumUp as the payment processor — we never see or store your card information. SumUp's privacy policy applies to payment data.
      </p>

      <h3 data-reveal class="font-display font-semibold text-[1.05rem] mt-6 mb-2">WhatsApp</h3>
      <p data-reveal class="text-muted text-[0.92rem] mb-4">
        Our WhatsApp links direct you to Meta's WhatsApp service. Any messages you send are subject to <strong class="text-dark">Meta's</strong> privacy policy. We use WhatsApp to communicate with you about classes, bookings, and enquiries.
      </p>

      <h2 data-reveal class="font-display font-semibold text-[1.25rem] mt-8 mb-3">Cookies</h2>
      <p data-reveal class="text-muted text-[0.92rem] mb-4">
        This website does not currently set any cookies. If we add analytics in the future, we will update this policy and add a consent mechanism where required.
      </p>

      <h2 data-reveal class="font-display font-semibold text-[1.25rem] mt-8 mb-3">Your rights</h2>
      <p data-reveal class="text-muted text-[0.92rem] mb-4">
        Under UK data protection law, you have the right to access, correct, or delete any personal data we hold about you. To make a request, email <a href="mailto:info@latinaddiction.co.uk" class="text-rose-dark font-semibold hover:underline">info@latinaddiction.co.uk</a>.
      </p>

      <h2 data-reveal class="font-display font-semibold text-[1.25rem] mt-8 mb-3">Contact</h2>
      <p data-reveal class="text-muted text-[0.92rem] mb-4">
        Data controller: Latin Addiction UK Ltd<br />
        Email: <a href="mailto:info@latinaddiction.co.uk" class="text-rose-dark font-semibold hover:underline">info@latinaddiction.co.uk</a>
      </p>

      <p data-reveal class="text-muted text-[0.82rem] mt-8">Last updated: April 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
